ed="T" n="0773b01"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0773b01"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000028637"><placeName>長沙</placeName><placeName>東寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010467">如會</persName><ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n2647"/>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0773b02"/><persName key="A010467">釋如會</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000030617"><placeName>韶州</placeName><placeName>始興</placeName></placeName>人也。<date from-iso="+0773-02-01" key="j20034242003806" to-iso="+0774-02-18"><name>大歷</name>八年</date>，止<persName key="A004218">國一<roleName>禪<lb
ed="T" n="0773b03"/>師</roleName></persName>門下，後歸<persName key="A003623">大寂</persName>法集。時禪客仰慕，決求心<lb
ed="T" n="0773b04"/>要，僧堂之內，床榻為之陷折，時號「折床會」，猶<lb
ed="T" n="0773b05"/>言鑿佛<anchor xml:id="beg0773003"/>床<anchor xml:id="end0773003"/>也。後徇請居<placeName key="PL000000028637"><placeName>長沙</placeName><placeName>東寺</placeName></placeName>焉。自<lb
ed="T" n="0773b06"/><persName key="A003623">大寂</persName>去世，其法門鼎盛，時無可敵，諺謂<placeName key="PL000000028637">東<lb
ed="T" n="0773b07"/>寺</placeName>為「禪窟」，斷可知矣。時相國<persName key="A010468">崔<roleName>公</roleName>群</persName><ptr target="#n1539"/>慕<persName key="A010467">會</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0773b08"/>之風，來謁于門，答對瀏<anchor xml:id="beg0773004"/>亮<anchor xml:id="end0773004"/>，辭咸造理。自爾<lb
ed="T" n="0773b09"/>為師友之契。初<persName key="A010468">群</persName>與<persName key="A010469">皇甫鎛</persName>議上<persName key="A002120">憲宗</persName>尊<lb
ed="T" n="0773b10"/>號，因被<persName key="A010469">鎛</persName>搆，出為<placeName key="PL000000028665">湖南</placeName>觀察<ptr target="#n1540"/>，閑豫歸心于<lb
ed="T" n="0773b11"/><persName key="A010467">會</persName>也。至<persName key="A004382">穆宗</persName><date from-iso="+0823-02-19" key="j20217042022057" to-iso="+0824-02-07"><name>長慶</name>癸卯歲</date>，終于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000028637">寺</ref>。春秋八<lb
ed="T" n="0773b12"/>十。時井泉預枯，異香馝馥，遷塔于城南。廉使<lb
ed="T" n="0773b13"/><persName key="A010395">李翱</persName>盡毀近城墳塔<ptr target="#n1541"/>，唯留<persName key="A010467">會</persName>所瘞浮圖，以<lb
ed="T" n="0773b14"/>筆題曰：「獨留此塔，以別賢愚矣。」<persName key="A010303">劉<roleName>膳部</roleName>軻</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0773b15"/>著碑焉。勅謚<persName key="A010467">傳明大師</persName>，塔曰<placeName>永際</placeName>。亦呼所<lb
ed="T" n="0773b16"/>居為「<persName key="A010467">夾山和尚</persName>」是歟<ptr target="#n1542"/>。</p>
